=head1 DESCRIPTION

Configuration to manage IoT Job's package version reporting. If
configured, Jobs updates the thing's reserved named shadow with the
package version information up on successful job completion.

B<Note:> For each job, the destinationPackageVersions attribute has to
be set with the correct data for Jobs to report to the thing shadow.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Enabled => Bool

Indicates whether the Job is enabled or not.


=head2 RoleArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the role that grants permission to
the IoT jobs service to update the reserved named shadow when the job
successfully completes.



